<h1>You Are Booked!</h1>

<div>
  <p>
    Congradulations!
  </p>

  <p>
    You are now booked for the trip, "<%= @trip.name %>", at <%= @trip.start_datetime.strftime("%m/%d/%y %I:%M %P") %>.
  </p>

  <p>
    If you have any questions for the driver, you can send a private message <%= link_to "here", new_message_path(:receiver => @trip.user.profile.id) %>.
    You will want to want to contact the driver to find out a pick up location, discuss compensation (gas money, snacks, etc), and any other question you
    might have for the ride.
  </p>

  <p>
    If you would like to send a message to the other riders in the trip, you can go <%= link_to 'here', trip_path(@trip) %> and enter a comment.  You can also go
    <%= link_to 'here', trip_path(@trip) %> to view more information about the trip.
  </p>

  <p>
    Thank you for using UrbanHitchhiker!
  </p>

</div>